properties.value: Cave entrances are pieces of scenery that can be used to enter dungeons all around the game. Most cave entrances have a unique object associated with them.

content:
Cave entrances are pieces of scenery that can be used to enter dungeons all around the game. Most cave entrances have a unique object associated with them.

Cave entrances are the method of entering the following dungeons or areas:

  • Brimstail's cave
  • Clivet's cave
  • Eagles' Peak dungeon
  • Elvarg's Den
  • Several dungeons in the Feldip Hills:
    • Corsair Cove Dungeon
    • Rantz's cave
    • Skavid caves
    • Toban's island
    • Ogre Enclave
  • Several caves found in the Fremennik region:
    • Fremennik Slayer Dungeon
    • Keldagrim cave
    • Lunar Isle Mine's deeper cave
    • The Kendal's cave
    • Waterbirth Dungeon
      • From Askeladden's location
  • Goblin Cave
  • Kraken Cove
  • Mor Ul Rek
  • Mos Le'Harmless Cave
  • The Hollows dungeon
  • Trahaearn mine
  • Several Troll Country caves:
    • Ice Path
    • Eadgar's cave
    • Saba's cave
    • Troll Arena
    • Trollweiss Dungeon
    • Weiss dungeon
  • TzHaar Fight Caves
  • The Underground Pass from the
    • Ardougne entrance
    • Tirannwn entrance
  • Ungael laboratory
  • Wyvern Cave

Or to exit the following caves:

  • Eagles' Peak dungeon
  • Ivandis Tomb
  • Ogre Enclave
  • TzHaar Fight Caves
  • Viyeldi caves

The following cave entrances act purely as decorative scenery, and cannot actually be entered:

  • South-east Wilderness
  • Lalli's cave
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
rawContent:
'''Cave entrances''' are pieces of scenery that can be used to enter [[dungeons]] all around the game. Most cave entrances have a unique object associated with them.

Cave entrances are the method of entering the following dungeons or areas:

* [[Cave entrance (Brimstail's cave)|Brimstail's cave]]
* [[Cave entrance (Clivet)|Clivet's cave]]
* [[Cave entrance (to Eagles' Peak dungeon)|Eagles' Peak dungeon]]
* [[Cave Entrance (Elvarg's Den)|Elvarg's Den]]
* Several dungeons in the [[Feldip Hills]]:
** [[Cave entrance (Corsair Cove Dungeon)|Corsair Cove Dungeon]]
** [[Cave entrance (Rantz's cave)|Rantz's cave]]
** [[Cave entrance (Skavid caves)|Skavid caves]]
** [[Cave entrance (Toban's island)|Toban's island]]
** [[Cave entrance (to Ogre Enclave)|Ogre Enclave]]
* Several caves found in the [[Fremennik]] region:
** [[Cave Entrance (Fremennik Slayer Dungeon)|Fremennik Slayer Dungeon]]
** [[Cave entrance (Keldagrim cave)|Keldagrim cave]]
** [[Cave entrance (Lunar Isle Mine)|Lunar Isle Mine]]'s deeper cave
** [[Cave entrance (The Kendal's cave)|The Kendal's cave]]
** [[Cave entrance (Waterbirth Dungeon)|Waterbirth Dungeon]]
*** [[Cave entrance (Askeladden)|From Askeladden's location]]
* [[Cave Entrance (Goblin Cave)|Goblin Cave]]
* [[Cave Entrance (Kraken Cove)|Kraken Cove]]
* [[Cave entrance (to Mor Ul Rek)|Mor Ul Rek]]
* [[Cave entrance (Mos Le'Harmless Cave)|Mos Le'Harmless Cave]]

* The [[Underground Pass]] from the

Or to exit the following caves:

The following cave entrances act purely as decorative scenery, and cannot actually be entered:
* [[Cave entrance (south-east Wilderness)|South-east Wilderness]]
